                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
                        <li class="mb-2">Designed and built with all the love in the world by the <a href="/" class="text-muted">Website team</a> with the help of <a href="/" class="text-muted">Our contributors</a>.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Code licensed <a href="/" target="_blank" rel="license noopener" class="text-muted">MIT</a>, docs <a href="/" target="_blank" rel="license noopener" class="text-muted">CC BY 3.0</a>.</li>
